Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.12,0:00:04.00,Memory,,0,0,0,,Fujiwarano Sai, a Go player from the Heian period
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.53,0:00:08.50,Memory,,0,0,0,,has passed through time and returned to\Nthe world in the mind of Shindou Hikaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.38,0:00:11.70,Memory,,0,0,0,,in order to obtain the Hand of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.47,0:01:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the Insei exams are going on today?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.41,0:01:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's taking it right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.93,0:01:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,A guy, probably a little younger than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.41,0:01:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.56,0:01:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,probably pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.28,0:01:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.97,0:01:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.52,0:02:06.48,Title_eps_top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(316,0)\fscx197\t(0,330,1,\fscx100)\blur0.8\pos(335,115)}The Twenty-Second Match
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.52,0:02:06.48,Title_eps,,0,0,0,,{\fad(274,0)\q2\blur0.8\fscy70\fscx333\t(0,330,1,\fscx100)\pos(325,365)}The Insei Examination
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.04,0:02:49.82,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.48,0:03:03.51,Sai,,0,0,0,,That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.33,0:03:09.09,Sai,,0,0,0,,He won't respond to that expansion. The Tsuke\Nyou played earlier was a mistake as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.22,0:03:14.30,Sai,,0,0,0,,The three stone advantage Hikaru\Nstarted with has already been spent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.16,0:03:18.20,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru is aware of that as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.47,0:03:21.30,Sai,,0,0,0,,That's why his game is getting\Nrushed and he's making mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.85,0:03:26.20,Sai,,0,0,0,,Against someone as strong as this person... he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.09,0:03:36.01,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru! You will lose at this rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.45,0:03:41.88,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru! If you wish, once again I will... Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.25,0:03:53.91,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.51,0:04:01.51,Sai,,0,0,0,,He can't hear me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.93,0:04:07.95,Sai,,0,0,0,,It's too bad that he doesn't have the\Nstrength to go along with his concentration.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.26,0:04:17.67,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I... I can't do it. I can't win.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.01,0:04:22.60,Thinking,,0,0,0,,If I go in too far, he'll crush me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.01,0:04:26.80,Thinking,,0,0,0,,But the gap will just keep on widening like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.06,0:04:32.90,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Touya...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.80,0:04:38.79,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Touya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.98,0:04:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.01,0:04:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get so nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.31,0:04:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to win to pass. I'm\Njust seeing how strong you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.36,0:04:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.38,0:04:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Couldn't you have said so earlier mister?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.78,0:05:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Mister!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.03,0:05:03.76,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru, mister is a little too rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.72,0:05:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.59,0:05:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What is with that posture!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.44,0:05:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.00,0:05:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,M-My legs are asleep... I can't hang on....
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.69,0:05:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Just say "excuse me" and\Nbreak your form in that case~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.45,0:05:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Couldn't you have said that earlier as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.77,0:05:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you look like you lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.35,0:05:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my third straight loss to Fuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.33,0:05:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm strong against Waya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.63,0:05:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm terrible against Fuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.24,0:05:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not good to think so negatively.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.69,0:05:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're terrible against Touya-kun too, Waya-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.22,0:06:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No one's good against Touya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.38,0:06:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... let's stop here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.86,0:06:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.24,0:06:19.66,Background,,0,0,0,,You should have simply pulled back\Nhere, that would've troubled white.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.31,0:06:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This formation is, a little difficult for black.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.44,0:06:30.22,Thinking,,0,0,0,,And? What is it? Did I pass? Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.35,0:06:43.49,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He's a little too weak, but it says here\Nhe's only been playing for a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.01,0:06:47.14,Thinking,,0,0,0,,That's some incredible growth,\Nreminiscent of Kurata 5dan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.47,0:06:53.93,Thinking,,0,0,0,,But, even Kurata-kun, who had a lot of talent,\Ngot a pro teacher right after he started playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.84,0:07:02.57,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He doesn't even have that. If he became\Nthis strong just from playing in a Jr. High\Nclub, he may have incredible potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.73,0:07:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true that you don't have a teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.19,0:07:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm... ahh... no...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.79,0:07:14.85,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Well, I kinda do... a totally useless one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.35,0:07:18.15,Sai,,0,0,0,,What! A totally what one, Hikaru!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.55,0:07:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But these three matches are...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.38,0:07:29.01,Background,,0,0,0,,you didn't read very deeply,\Nand your play is very careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.35,0:07:31.82,Background,,0,0,0,,Oh? They're all from the same day?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.82,0:07:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I played it simultaneously.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.81,0:07:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the first time I played three\Ngames simultaneously, it was horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.90,0:07:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Th...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.72,0:07:51.38,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Three games!? And it was his first time!?\NHe played this well on his first try!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.60,0:07:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Come here starting next\Nmonth. Go get your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.31,0:08:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.28,0:08:02.63,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.35,0:08:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the central room. Looks\Nlike most of the matches are over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.20,0:08:18.10,Background,,0,0,0,,What about a furikawari here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.10,0:08:19.81,Background,,0,0,0,,That might work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.21,0:08:21.37,Background,,0,0,0,,Mark me down too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.69,0:08:23.81,Background,,0,0,0,,This is your fourth straight win, Matsura!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.44,0:08:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there are kids younger than\NHikaru. No wonder he passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.71,0:08:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a pairings sheet over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.58,0:08:38.43,Sai,,0,0,0,,Oh! Hikaru! Let's look over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.81,0:08:39.84,Thinking,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.37,0:08:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you do if he played here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.39,0:08:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad for black.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.88,0:08:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What about a tsuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.55,0:08:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just pull back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.46,0:08:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That might be too soft...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.01,0:08:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you pass?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.58,0:08:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.95,0:09:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You came to take the Insei exam?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.81,0:09:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Waya do you know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.53,0:09:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I heard him say "To surpass\NTouya Akira" in the hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.17,0:09:15.96,Background,,0,0,0,,I used to say that too when I first joined.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.26,0:09:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You got a problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.90,0:09:22.29,Background,,0,0,0,,I played Touya twice during the\Npro exam, but I don't like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.81,0:09:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You played Touya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.35,0:09:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you? Have you played him before?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.13,0:09:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, during a team match for my Go club.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.51,0:09:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He was in the Kaiou Jr. High's Go club and...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.91,0:09:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Go club? Touya!? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.64,0:09:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember hearing Mr. Kuwabara laugh\Nabout it with Mr. Nishio a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.12,0:09:46.86,Background,,0,0,0,,About how the Meijin's son was participating\Nin a tournament with his Jr. High's Go club.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.52,0:09:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh so it's for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.70,0:09:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.10,0:09:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What an incredible first board\Nmatch for a Go club match.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.70,0:09:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Between a soon-to-be Insei and Touya Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.61,0:10:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope. It was a third board match.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.61,0:10:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Third board!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.66,0:10:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't strong enough to\Nplay first board back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.33,0:10:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That may have been the case with you,\Nbut Touya? Third board? Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.67,0:10:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He forced the teacher to make him third\Nboard because he wanted to play against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.98,0:10:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Forced?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.14,0:10:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said, that's the kind of guy he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.10,0:10:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason he joined the Go club\Nwas just to play against me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.92,0:10:24.56,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.67,0:10:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru, let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.22,0:10:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll start coming here starting\Nnext month. Nice to meet all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.73,0:10:52.54,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Oh crap...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.44,0:11:00.52,Background,,0,0,0,,Touya Akira's what!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.92,0:11:02.41,Background,,0,0,0,,Rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.77,0:11:03.64,Background,,0,0,0,,Rival?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.06,0:11:05.56,Background,,0,0,0,,Morning, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.73,0:11:10.26,Background,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, the guy coming today,\Nhe might be really strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.73,0:11:13.86,Background,,0,0,0,,Touya Akira supposedly went to a\NGo club tournament pursuing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.61,0:11:17.65,Background,,0,0,0,,And he...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.43,0:11:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.74,0:11:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Mo...rning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.81,0:11:39.83,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sai? Isn't everyone glaring at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.85,0:11:43.62,Sai,,0,0,0,,They probably think a horribly\Nstrong enemy's arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.06,0:11:47.43,Sai,,0,0,0,,It's all because you talked about Touya, Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.93,0:11:49.93,Thinking,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.55,0:11:55.86,Background,,0,0,0,,Did you hear? The guy coming today.\NYeah! I heard my parents talking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.51,0:11:59.28,Background,,0,0,0,,Touya Akira views him as a rival!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.80,0:12:01.44,Background,,0,0,0,,He's in the seventh grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.91,0:12:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm playing him for my first match today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.82,0:12:07.20,Background,,0,0,0,,He's probably really strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.46,0:12:12.74,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Tsk... they were talking about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.42,0:12:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm... who's Uchida?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.59,0:12:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.74,0:12:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We're playing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.97,0:12:24.28,Thinking,,0,0,0,,A girl!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.70,0:12:27.74,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I got a pairings chart, but it only has last names.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.28,0:12:37.31,Thinking,,0,0,0,,She's fifth in the second class. I'm\N25th. I'm starting at the very bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.20,0:12:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this room just for the second class?\NAre there first class people here too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.29,0:12:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all here. That half is the first class.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.90,0:13:05.60,Sai,,0,0,0,,You can rise up to first class\Nif you're strong enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.13,0:13:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.76,0:13:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So second class isn't good enough for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.29,0:13:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't feel that way at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.78,0:13:53.48,Thinking,,0,0,0,,It's not that second class isn't good enough for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.82,0:13:57.53,Thinking,,0,0,0,,But Touya is above first class,\Nwhich is above second class.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.26,0:14:05.32,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I passed the Insei exam! I'm not\Nlike I was in the Go club anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.79,0:14:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I resign.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.27,0:14:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.13,0:14:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh! I totally read that part wrong!\NI'm such an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.10,0:14:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, I wonder if his game is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.20,0:14:34.38,Background,,0,0,0,,You can't get any eyes with this shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.10,0:14:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,In this situation, if you cut them...\Nyou can target this area better.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.46,0:14:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This made black lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.41,0:14:48.36,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Looks like he lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.06,0:14:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,How'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.63,0:14:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Uchida won
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.57,0:14:56.95,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord1\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1}The Second Match
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.00,0:15:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I resign.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.38,0:15:11.75,Thinking,,0,0,0,,And he's Touya's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.17,0:15:13.12,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Rival?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.23,0:15:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Moving into here, I think that\Nwas a little unreasonable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.10,0:15:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.54,0:15:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this happened, right?\NEven if you moved here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.74,0:15:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you'd get crushed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.36,0:15:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be bad even if it went like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.24,0:15:30.45,Background,,0,0,0,,There's nothing you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.05,0:15:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Two straight losses...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.91,0:15:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing to fear from here it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.08,0:15:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he's just nervous since it's his first day?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.40,0:15:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Then wanna watch over him a little longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.55,0:15:55.10,Background,,0,0,0,,Waya, wanna go get lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.13,0:16:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing for lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.06,0:16:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm buying it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.40,0:16:09.91,Note,,0,0,0,,[note: Loae's Japanese 101\NObento = Lunch Box\NOnigiri = Rice ball\NKeep learning, and you too can be as l33t as Loae]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.40,0:16:09.91,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord1\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(232,304)}Obento Onigiri
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.99,0:16:09.32,Background,,0,0,0,,Thank you. Come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.45,0:16:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}What's your relationship with Touya?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.37,0:16:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Were you his classmate in elementary school?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.41,0:16:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you played him in a match\Nin a go tournament for your club.\NBut why a school tournament?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.59,0:16:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Touya pursue you? That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.45,0:16:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not strong at all. Are you really rivals?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.36,0:16:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Really! I'm his, and he's my rival!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.58,0:16:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There's too much of a gap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.01,0:16:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll catch up eventually!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.49,0:16:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the reason for Touya\Nthinking of you as a rival?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.08,0:16:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He saw my incredible potential at Go,\Nand that's why he views me as a rival!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.04,0:17:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Your potential at Go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.03,0:17:04.59,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru, that was cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.40,0:17:08.78,Sai,,0,0,0,,But... that's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.43,0:17:11.70,Thinking,,0,0,0,,That doesn't matter, I'll make it come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.46,0:17:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Something else you want to ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.61,0:17:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,How was the match against Kaiou?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.44,0:17:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,3-0 loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.97,0:17:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Touya is special, but everyone\Nelse in Kaiou is also strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.36,0:17:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard Kaiou's Go club is strong, but wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.41,0:17:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaiou's president's really strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.29,0:17:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried playing against him in a Go\NSalon another day, but I totally lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.44,0:17:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not because he's strong,\Nthat's because you suck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.10,0:17:59.11,Background,,0,0,0,,Waaahhh! I hit the wrong button!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.16,0:18:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Isumi-san! A coffee came\Nout! You drink it Isumi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.56,0:18:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.08,0:18:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Drink it? But it's black!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.96,0:18:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the oldest... but Black is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.02,0:18:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Waya...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.08,0:18:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.58,0:18:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll give it to the teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.80,0:18:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Black coffee, that reminds me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.50,0:18:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember that guy that used to drink\NBlack Coffee? In the seventh grade!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.13,0:18:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah! He used to come\Nhere. What was his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.63,0:18:35.67,Sai,,0,0,0,,What's a "Black Coffee" Hikaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.19,0:18:37.32,Thinking,,0,0,0,,It's really bitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.25,0:18:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of a guy would drink Black Coffee\Nin the seventh grade? Was he good at go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.68,0:18:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all! He was here for a year, and then quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.30,0:18:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Was he always second class?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.41,0:18:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope. He rose up to first class\Nonce. I remember playing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.84,0:18:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, I played him too. He wasn't any good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.86,0:18:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I beat him too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.99,0:19:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You've both been in the first class since back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.96,0:19:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Being in first class for a long\Ntime isn't something to be proud of.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.57,0:19:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,When are we finally going to\Npass the pro exam, Waya?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.71,0:19:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what that guy that got\Npummeled in first class is doing now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.95,0:19:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He was really smart!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.26,0:19:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, he went to Kaiou Jr.\NHigh. What was his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.54,0:19:28.12,Background,,0,0,0,,He was tall and wore glasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.23,0:19:29.56,Background,,0,0,0,,He should be in the ninth grade right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.48,0:19:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I remember! It's Kishimoto! Kishimoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.36,0:19:37.70,Background,,0,0,0,,Back then it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.76,0:19:40.16,Background,,0,0,0,,He didn't look like a Jr. High student.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.14,0:19:42.45,Background,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, and
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.74,0:19:44.50,Background,,0,0,0,,And those glasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.28,0:19:47.50,Background,,0,0,0,,He's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:51.96,Background,,0,0,0,,It was total domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.13,0:19:53.91,Background,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.18,0:19:57.89,Background,,0,0,0,,But he doesn't look like a Jr. High student.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.26,0:20:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.29,0:20:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.11,0:20:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, that strong first board from Kaiou\Nyou were talking about. What's his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.32,0:20:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.78,0:20:32.83,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Kaiou's first board was... Kishimoto\Nwas... always second class...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.55,0:20:38.98,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I... I... will I ever be able to make it to first class?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.72,0:22:12.32,NoteTimes,,0,0,0,,{\fs32.5\pos(320,356)}Umezawa Yukari's Go Go Igo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.32,0:22:15.76,NoteTimes,,0,0,0,,{\fs32.5\pos(320,308)}Sagamihara South Kamimizo\NPrivate Jr. High School
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.04,0:22:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}We're at South Kamimizo Private Jr.\NHigh school in Sagamihara city today.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.46,0:22:20.35,NoteTimes,,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs32.5\pos(231,469)}Mai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.46,0:22:20.35,NoteTimes,,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs32.5\pos(420,469)}Teacher  Yukari
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.39,0:22:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Teacher Yukari immediately\Nstarted playing five games at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.48,0:22:40.02,Note,,0,0,0,,{\q2\fs30\bord1\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\move(2135,433,-1512,433)}Kanagawa Prefecture Sagamihara city South Kamimizo Jr. High School Go-Shougi club. Formed in 1998. 15 members. Record for 2001: 7th in the prefecture - East Japan Tournament, 9th in the upper class - Prefecture Rookie Tournament second place.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.61,0:22:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I also played someone on a 9x9 board.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.87,0:22:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Have I gotten stronger than before?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.15,0:22:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Don't let your stones get cut apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.49,0:22:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The teacher gave them some\Nadvice after the games.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.17,0:22:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Which one to take is up to you but,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.06,0:22:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(372,460)}Most of the kids here have been playing\Ngo for less than a year. But they're really
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.22,0:22:51.11,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs31\bord1\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(101,41)}Y\No\Nu\Nr\Nc\No\Nm\Nm\Ne\Nn\Nt\N!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.56,0:22:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(372,460)}strong and they surprised me.\NA second or third Hikaru may\Nnot be out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.35,0:22:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Please enjoy Go in the future as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.03,0:22:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.10,0:22:57.32,NoteTimes,,0,0,0,,{\fs32.5\pos(168,368)}Thanks to everyone in\Nthe South Kainan Jr.\NHigh Go-Shougi club.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.10,0:22:57.32,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord1\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(507,433)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.03,0:23:02.02,Background,,0,0,0,,He came to see if I was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.58,0:23:07.20,Background,,0,0,0,,He said he'd never appear before\Nme again... he's waiting for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.26,0:23:10.50,Background,,0,0,0,,Pursue me with his skills?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.91,0:23:12.04,Background,,0,0,0,,That's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.55,0:23:26.55,Background,,0,0,0,,I'll go far beyond him then,\Nwhere he can't possibly reach me.
