Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.00,0:00:14.87,Op1English,,0,0,0,,Now you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.87,0:00:16.71,Op1English,,0,0,0,,holding me up strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.98,0:00:18.87,Op1English,,0,0,0,,Now I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.87,0:00:20.71,Op1English,,0,0,0,,holding you up as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.85,0:00:26.73,Op1English,,0,0,0,,So let us now, while wandering live together
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.94,0:00:29.41,Op1English,,0,0,0,,towards the future
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.95,0:00:40.67,Op1English,,0,0,0,,Even when I'm capricing with my friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.96,0:00:44.77,Op1English,,0,0,0,,I feel an emptiness in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.89,0:00:46.70,Op1English,,0,0,0,,Looked at with cold eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.99,0:00:51.90,Op1English,,0,0,0,,I'm blown by the wind of a dry age
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.38,0:00:56.60,Op1English,,0,0,0,,Feelings of doubt and courage
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.60,0:01:00.25,Op1English,,0,0,0,,are back to back
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.94,0:01:08.94,Op1English,,0,0,0,,but I'll make these dreams come true now with my own hands.
