Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.20,0:20:48.40,Ed2English,,0,0,0,,I thought that someone would bring me,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.30,0:20:56.10,Ed2English,,0,0,0,,the happiness that I dreamed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.35,0:20:59.28,Ed2English,,0,0,0,,In a quick paced city,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.89,0:21:02.55,Ed2English,,0,0,0,,all I'm doing is listing off excuses,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.40,0:21:09.70,Ed2English,,0,0,0,,and lying to myself, that everyone was doing the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.99,0:21:17.20,Ed2English,,0,0,0,,Are you really satisfied right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.51,0:21:25.68,Ed2English,,0,0,0,,It feels as if you've straight through my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.68,0:21:29.20,Ed2English,,0,0,0,,If i had not met you,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.44,0:21:32.53,Ed2English,,0,0,0,,I would still only have a false smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.76,0:21:36.40,Ed2English,,0,0,0,,My words and disagreements
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.50,0:21:39.70,Ed2English,,0,0,0,,would only have been superficial.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.80,0:21:43.47,Ed2English,,0,0,0,,With the power of your gaze,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.47,0:21:46.70,Ed2English,,0,0,0,,I am starting to change!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.80,0:21:50.40,Ed2English,,0,0,0,,In order to cast off
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.50,0:21:54.70,Ed2English,,0,0,0,,the swaying feelings of yesterday.
